                    </h2>
                    <hr>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-8">
                    <iframe width="100%" src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d15919.28138775457!2d9.7482151!3d4.057026!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x10610dbdc43636c7%3A0x2f7209fea45ab7a7!2sRoyal+Bilingual+College+Ndogbong!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sfr!4v1440499945088" width="100%" height="400" frameborder="0" style="border:0" allowfullscreen marginwidth="0"></iframe>
